@dan77062, thanks for reporting the issue. See pull request #77.


The `laser_enabled` and `kinect_enabled` parameters shouldn't be used. Instead, you should use the appropriate environment variables for choosing your sensor configuration. See [this](#!/osrf/subt/wiki/api) document for further information. I removed them from the urdf.

Similarly, I removed the localization node. This shouldn't be part of the minimum example that we want to provide. Robot localization falls under the responsibility of each participant.
